## Legal compliance

We comply with the laws of every country in which we operate. Where the laws of two countries conflict, we comply with the stricter and document the reason in the *Decision Log*.

We do not interpret the law informally. Where a question has legal consequence — a contract, a privacy decision, an employment matter — we take advice from a qualified professional. The cost of advice is recorded in the budget; the absence of advice is recorded as a risk.

